OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunny spells,
OL,7,Fbut turning cloudier for Shetland. The
OL,8,Frest of the night will be dry and
OL,9,Fbreezy with cloud becoming widespread.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA cloudy but mostly dry
OL,12,Fmorning ahead of patchy light rain
OL,13,Fspreading north in the afternoon.
OL,14,FStrong southeasterly winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,18,For a few longer spells of rain, some
OL,19,Fof which may be on the heavy side.
OL,20,FRisk of sea mist and fog at times.
